  "message": "Retarget submodule from claude-pa-matrix-bot to bot-toolkit\n\n- Replace lib/claude-pa-matrix-bot submodule with lib/bot-toolkit\n  pointing to prime-radiant-inc/bot-toolkit standalone repo\n- Update package.json dep path to file:./lib/bot-toolkit\n- Update sync-toolkit script for new submodule path\n- Update check-submodule.yml for new path\n- Update CLAUDE.md references\n\nImport name stays 'bot-toolkit' \u2014 no source changes needed.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
